content:
Warmup:
Mobility (shoulders, hips, ankles)

Metcon:
AMRAP in 3min:
5 OHS (#40/20)
5 OTB Burpees

Rest 2min

AMRAP in 3min:
5 Front Squats (#50/30)
5 OTB Burpees

Rest 6min

In teams of 3:
AMRAP in 6min:
Back Squats (#60/40)
*use human racks - two partners holding the bar while the third does the squats. alternate partners as needed.*
